game.twenty_four.details:
f%The 24 Game, calculate 24 by combining numbers with basic arithmetic symbols.

{tc:yellow}Items:{tc:clear}
{tc:light_cyan}+ - * / (){tc:clear} Basic arithmetic symbols

{tc:yellow}Modes:{tc:clear}
{tc:light_cyan}Symbol Mode{tc:clear}: Place the four basic arithmetic symbols + - * /
{tc:light_cyan}Parenthesis Mode{tc:clear}: Place or delete the basic arithmetic symbols ( )
{tc:light_cyan}Number Mode{tc:clear}: Adjust number positions and modify the positive/negative sign of numbers

{tc:yellow}Difficulty:{tc:clear}
{tc:light_cyan}Classic Mode:{tc:clear} Only positive numbers
{tc:light_cyan}Fixed Negative Mode:{tc:clear} Includes positive and negative numbers, signs cannot be modified
{tc:light_cyan}Variable Negative Mode:{tc:clear} Includes positive and negative numbers, signs can be modified

{tc:yellow}Modify Difficulty (P command):{tc:clear}
{tc:light_cyan}Mode:{tc:clear} 1-3
